Package: fungitax
Type: Package
Title: A package for updating and resolving fungal names based on Index Fungorum
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Albert Morera <morera.marra@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Albert Morera <morera.marra@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows for the retrieval and updating of fungal names from Index Fungorum, including synonyms and taxonomic classification.
